com.xxdb

类 DBConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xxdb.DBConnection

  • public class DBConnection
extends Object
    Sets up a connection to DolphinDB server through TCP/IP protocol Executes DolphinDB scripts

    Example:

    import com.xxdb; DBConnection conn = new DBConnection(); boolean success = conn.connect("localhost", 8080); conn.run("sum(1..100)");
